title: Carried Away
info:
3rd in streaming music competition at Revision 2014

I got carried away
on a summer day
no more pain no more decay
I will never turn away
 
so many things to say
on a summer day
all I want is you to stay with me
I'll never turn away
 
I'll never let you down
 
I'll never change the way
it used to be
it's neither status 
nor esprit
 
cuz 
 
i got carried away
